OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 05 MAR
OL,4,CEVENTS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1999FTrevor McDonald presents the
OL,7,Ffinal edition of ITV News at Ten,
OL,8,Fbefore the programme is moved to a
OL,9,Flater timeslot.
OL,10,
OL,11,FIt includes a report by Norman Rees
OL,12,Fabout the major news stories covered by
OL,13,Fthe programme over the past thirty
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,15,
OL,16,FITV News at Ten returned in January
OL,17,F2001.
